quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  42,52,aur isi terhan hum ne apne hukum se tumhari taraf rooh al quds ke zariye se ( quran ) bheja hai. tum nah to kitaab ko jantay they aur nah imaan ko. lekin hum ne is ko noor banaya hai ke is se hum apne bundon mein se jis ko chahtay hain hadaayat karte hain. aur be shak ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum seedha rasta dikhata ho
  42,53,( yani ) khuda ka rasta jo asmano aur zameen ki sab cheezon ka maalik hai. dekho sab kaam khuda ki taraf rujoo hon ge ( aur wohi un mein faisla kere ga )
  43,1,Haa-Meeem
  43,2,kitaab roshan ki qasam
  43,3,ke hum ne is ko quran arabi banaya hai taakay tum samjhoo
  43,4,aur yeh barri kitaab ( yani looh mehfooz ) mein hamaray paas ( likhi hui aur ) barri fazeelat aur hikmat wali hai
  43,5,bhala is liye ke tum hadd se niklay hue log ho hum tum ko nasiyaat karne se baz rahen ge
  43,6,aur hum ne pehlay logon mein bhi bohat se paighambar beje they
  43,7,aur koi paighambar un ke paas nahi aata tha magar woh is se tamaskhur karte they
  43,8,to jo un mein sakht zor walay they un ko hum ne halaak kardiya aur aglay logon ki haalat guzar gayi
  43,9,aur agar tum un se pucho ke asmano aur zameen ko kis ne pedakiya hai to keh den ge ke un ko ghalib aur ilm walay ( khuda ) ne pedakiya hai
  43,10,jis ne tumahray liye zameen ko bichona banaya. aur is mein tumahray liye raste banaye taakay tum raah maloom karo
